            <div class="article_col-main article_col-main-left article_main">
              <div class="article-body" itemprop="articleBody">
                    <p> President Obama joined the growing chorus Wednesday condemning Sen. Ted Cruz for calling on cops to &quot;patrol and secure Muslim neighborhoods&quot; in the wake of the Belgian terror attacks. </p>
                
              
              
              
                    <p> Speaking in Argentina, Obama said that strategy &quot;makes no sense.&quot; </p>
                
              
              
              
                
              
              
              
                
                
                
                
                
                
                
                    <div class="js-player-shell" data-playertype="Inline">
                      <div class="widget widget_video widget_trusted">
                          <div class="video-viewport">
